_sText:
This map has 5 areas.
-Moving targets shooting range (Inside blue warehouse)
-Still target shooting range (Inside white warehouse)
-Sniper area (with maximum distance wich counter-strike bullets can fly) behind white warehouse
-Grenade area with grenade dispenser behind blue warehouse
-Reaction and shooting track on timer.

Targets can be spawned and respawned by pressing area's buttons.
